op align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Pet Discipline or Elemental Pact</span><hr size=1> If you still tend to solo/partner alot, Pet Discipline is a must have. It's alot easier for you to pull if you don't have to spam /pet back off on your way back to your group or pet. I'm currently 2-1/2 points into purchasing Pet Discipline and I'm really looking forward to it. I'll probably get Elemental Pact next then get SCM3 and SCF3. <p><br>
