<br>
Some tips about how to do it most efficiently:<br>
<br>
1) Make sure the other pets have taunt off.<br>
<br>
2) Make sure the owner of those pet send their pet from the back of the mob.<br>
<br>
3) Use air pet, it's our best tank, and stun + taunt + initial aggro will make sure he keeps aggro the whole fight.<br>
<br>
